= Maintenance
This application depends on many plugins. 
Those plugins other than home brewed ones, managed with 'git submodule', may be need update by re-installing.
To update plugins:

 script/plugin install --force {URL}

== home brewed

script-refactor.git
 Provides script/refactor.

